verse.lines:
{lang-eng}I've found the pearl of greatest price,
My heart doth sing for joy:
And sing I must, a Christ I have;
O what a Christ have I?{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}My Christ he is the Lord of lords,
He is the King of kings;
He is the Sun of righteousness,
With healing in his wings.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}My Christ, he is the Tree of Life,
Which in God's garden grows;
Whose fruit does feed, whose leaves do heal;
My Christ is Sharon's rose.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Christ is my father, and my friend,
My brother and my love;
My head, my hope, my counselor,
My advocate above.{/lang-eng}
